Package: open.gismo
Title: Open-Source Analytics Platform Powered by workr
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
        "Jeremy",
        "Wildfire",
        email = "jeremy_wildfire@example.com",
        role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: A thin integration layer over {workr} that connects four modular
    components — Database, Analytics Engine, Web Front-end, and Config — into an
    end-to-end analytics platform. The default implementation uses GitHub as the
    backbone: repos and releases for storage, GitHub Actions for compute, GitHub
    Pages for the front-end, and YAML files in repos for configuration.
